RACE.FOOTNOTES: MAGIC CARPET settled last but one racing inside, saved ground through the turn and put to urging at the top of the stretch, drove past along the inside seventy yards from home. MUCHO BLING switched off the inside, trailed up the backstretch, failed to menace.
